snippet.title: Fantasian Neo Dimension - Release Date Announcement Trailer | PS5 & PS4 Games
snippet.description:
https://store.playstation.com/en-us/concept/10010526

FANTASIAN Neo Dimension is available for pre-order on PS5™ and PS4™ today, launching on December 5th, 2024.

The Father of FINAL FANTASY, Hironobu Sakaguchi, and renowned composer Nobuo Uematsu return to deliver an original RPG story.

Embark on an multi-dimensional journey to reclaim your lost memories and save the world from the mechteria infection. 

#ps5 #ps5games #ps4 #ps4games #stateofplay #fantasian
